section.p:
You can also run analysis on records within the bucket. The following query returns
                the number of types in the travel-sample
                bucket:>>> for row in cb.n1ql_query("SELECT DISTINCT(type) FROM `travel-sample`"):
...   print row
... 
{u'type': u'route'}
{u'type': u'airport'}
{u'type': u'airline'}
{u'type': u'landmark'}
